         <abstract id="aspace_d8eeca68e00de18b2f315feac24326bd">Ephemera related to the 2017 Catalan Independence Referendum, Declaration of Independence, and related elections. Ephemera includes cloth banners and bags, newspapers, pamphlets, and posters.</abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_d8d3cad8b1370f1f55d9d38c553de184">
            <language>The materials are in Catalan and Spanish.</language>
         </langmaterial>
      </did>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_1d43bb48a1c13709253b813a7a265aaa">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Ephemera related to the 2017 Catalan Independence Referendum, Declaration of Independence, and related elections. Ephemera includes cloth banners and bags, newspapers, pamphlets, stickers, and posters.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_4a32b92db109fb7ca68a4369968a70a3">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Transferred by the Librarian for the Latin American and Iberian Collections, 2018.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <bioghist id="aspace_6a124d590e7f881af393f990d051b04c">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Catalan separatists movement protests affected Spain in 2017.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <custodhist id="aspace_f2024aeb04e2364555e4307253a03bb0">
         <head>Custodial History</head>
         <p>Materials were collected by the Librarian for the Latin American and Iberian Collections.</p>  
      </custodhist>
      <userestrict id="aspace_03d95cdb696e922e0ac32e19f5093b92">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright status for collection materials is unknown. Transmission or reproduction of materials protected by U.S. Copyright Law (Title 17, U.S.C.) beyond that allowed by fair use requires the written permission of the copyright owners. Works not in the public domain cannot be commercially exploited without permission of the copyright owners. Responsibility for any use rests exclusively with the user.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_dc9037846f3f3f36212ea2ff517d1d77">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Materials are arranged by format type.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_298521a1e1f4398ae756fe5ebc7c68e9">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_f06fc238e08816d7900f10b354e3596f">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Catalunya Independence Movement Ephemera (MS 2099). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
